text: Tomaž Dolar (born 27 October 1966) is a Slovenian ski jumper. He competed in the large hill event at the 1984 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Yugoslavia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1984 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Jesenice, Jesenice
